Paragraph: By means of technological skills, Nisar Aziz Agri-Tech Center at Namal Institute is all set to revolutionize the rural landscape of Pakistan through two of its initiatives; ‘Meri Fasal’.
Electrical engineers, Asif Ahmed and Muhammad Iqbal, have collectively developed a solar powered car which can go up to 50 km per hour.
Rahnumai, a social enterprise movement is all set to revolutionize Pakistan’s educational system.
Atif Rafiq graduated from Namal Institute in 2014 and even after so many years he still relishes his most prized moments at his alma mater.
